description: A mobile-friendly web application for Taazabites, a premium healthy food delivery service in Bangalore. It features a powerful AI-powered meal planner using the Gemini API to generate personalized meal plans, suggest dish alternatives for various dietary needs like keto and high-protein, and provide corporate wellness solutions.
